{{Noticebox/Community}}
'''Wickerbeast''' is an open species and [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatars|avatar]] base originating from the furry fandom, featuring reptilian, troll-like creatures from the fictional world of Osova. The species was originally created by Daemon_Lady (Simone White) in 2013 and is currently managed by PineWarden. The species lore encompasses a detailed fictional world with its own religions, language, currency, and cultural traditions. Several VRChat-ready avatar models based on the Wickerbeast have been created by independent artists, making it one of the recognizable furry avatar species in VRChat alongside the [[Community:Rexouium|Rexouium]].

== World of Osova ==

Wickerbeasts inhabit a fictional world called '''Osova''', home to various species collectively referred to as "the Fera." The world features its own geography, languages, religions, and cultural systems. Creators can choose whether their Wickerbeast characters exist within the official Osova canon or in their own independent lore.

Osova is populated by several other species alongside Wickerbeasts, including the '''Etekoi''', a lemur-like anthropomorphic species with elemental powers over fire, ice, and wind, as well as healing abilities. Domesticated fauna include '''Oshari''' (two-legged, cow-like creatures raised for food, heavy lifting, and travel with plated faces and three eyes) and '''Skitadel''' (four-legged, lizard-like mounts that are the natural predator of Oshari).

=== Language and currency ===

Wickerbeasts use a written language called '''Vaeick''', a 26-sign alphabet of strokes, lines, and dots originally developed so that Wickerbeasts could carve stories into stone using their claws. The language uses signs that loosely resemble the Latin alphabet and is written in English.

The Wickerbeast currency is called '''Vipera''' (symbol: Ꞩ), named after the god of prosperity. Coins come in gold denominations (Ꞩ100, Ꞩ50, Ꞩ20) and silver denominations (Ꞩ10, Ꞩ5, Ꞩ1, Ꞩ0.50, Ꞩ0.25). High-value coins sometimes feature collectible designs on the reverse side.

== Species design ==

Wickerbeasts are large, muscular reptilian creatures characterized by a set of mandatory anatomical traits that all designs must follow. The species is open, meaning anyone can create their own Wickerbeast character as long as these core traits are respected.

* Backward-facing ears
* Pupil-less eyes
* Jagged jaw structure with serrated teeth
* Four-clawed hands and three-toed feet
* Short fur with patches of longer fur (mane-like hair)
* Horns (growing from the skull)

=== Subtypes ===

The species includes several subtypes, each with distinct physical characteristics and roles within Osova. The original four subtypes (Standard, King, Swamp, and Rogue) were introduced between 2013 and 2014. Three additional subtypes were added between 2019 and 2022: Aerions (created by Daemon_Lady) and Dwellers and Pelagics (created by PineWarden).

